# Shape — environment variables
#
# Shape is a key-in-localStorage app: drafts live in the browser and export
# to JSON / PDF. No env required for the playgrounds, studio, or notebook to
# work locally.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Linear feedback (POST /api/feedback). When both vars below are set, the
# floating "Feedback" button in the bottom-right files a ticket in Linear.
# Without them the endpoint returns 503 and the modal shows a clear
# "not configured" message — local dev still works.

# Personal API key — Linear settings → API → Personal API keys. Keep secret;
# this is server-side only, never exposed to the browser.
LINEAR_API_KEY=

# UUID of the team the feedback tickets should land in. Find via Linear
# settings → API, or run a `teams { nodes { id name } }` query.
LINEAR_TEAM_ID=
